title: Gravitro v1.0 [PD]
description:
Treat yourself to a cute fantastic gravity game!

Gravitro is an arcade puzzle game where you control the gravity to help the lost pink space cupcake to reach the rainbow ring!!

Press the planets(Grivo and Kravo) to turn on gravity, 
Release to turn off gravity!
40 games and more coming in the future versions!

What's New:
